getToKnowMe.title: Broker / Owner
getToKnowMe.description: At Corcoran Prestige Realty, we’ve built more than a company—we’ve cultivated a family dedicated to raising each other up. Our commitment goes far beyond transactions; it’s about making a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve. We have embraced a culture where every interaction is an opportunity to support, uplift, and positively impact those around us. Since 2011, our team has been more than just professionals; we are a group of individuals who care deeply about the people we work with and the neighborhoods we serve. Whether we’re helping you find your dream home or navigate the complexities of the market, our goal is simple: to be genuinely helpful, every step of the way. We’re not just building a business, we’re building a community where kindness, support, and dedication lead the way.

reviews.reviewComment: We were first time homebuyers with zero knowledge of this whole process. Alexis helped us understand each step we were going through and was so patient and understanding from touring homes (lots of homes) to the application and closing process. She was always available for us when we had questions or wanting to tour more houses, even when she was on vacation! She was super relatable and we felt so comfortable with her despite the uncomfortable unknown of buying a house. I’ve already passed her info along to friends who are even considering buying a home cause she’s that great! We’re so thankful for her!
reviews.workDescription: Bought a Single Family home in 2024 in Annalea kingspark, Friendswood, TX.

reviews.reviewComment: Paul delivered an exceptional home-buying experience from start to finish. As first-time buyers, we began the process with uncertainty, but his professionalism, expertise, and calm, confident guidance immediately put us at ease. Every interaction was handled with precision, transparency, and genuine care. Paul anticipated our needs, communicated clearly, and ensured no detail was overlooked. What could have felt overwhelming was instead seamless and thoughtfully managed. His commitment to excellence is unmistakable, and we are truly grateful for his guidance. We would confidently recommend Paul to anyone seeking a realtor who offers a polished, high-caliber experience.
She's awesome and active respect her career, she helped us to find our home easily, we appreciate her support and the hard work with us she's doing great and she helped us to find the correct choice.
reviews.workDescription: Bought a Single Family home in 2025 in Katy, TX.

reviews.reviewComment: Working with Alex was A great experience. He was patient, supportive, and always had our best interests in mind. No question ever went unanswered, and they made the entire process feel easy and enjoyable. We are so grateful for his hard work and would absolutely recommend them to family and friends.
reviews.workDescription: Bought a Single Family home in 2025 in Crosby, TX.

reviews.reviewComment: Look, if you're navigating the Houston real estate market, Mandy is the person you want in your corner. She’s not just a real estate agent; she's genuinely on your team, making what can be a totally stressful process feel surprisingly smooth. Clients constantly mention how patient Mandy is, ensuring you know exactly what's happening at every stage, so you never feel left in the dark. People describe her as incredibly knowledgeable and super hands-on. She’s apparently got a background in law, which definitely shines through in how she handles negotiations and paperwork, fighting hard for her clients to get the best deal. You get the sense she really cares, taking the time to figure out what you actually want—your budget, your must-haves, everything. That personalized attention makes you feel like you're her number one priority. She’s professional, sharp, quick to respond, and goes above and beyond what you’d expect from a typical agent. The overwhelming theme in her reviews is that she somehow manages to turn buying or selling a house from an anxiety-inducing nightmare into a positive, even exciting, experience. Her positive energy is contagious and keeps the whole process moving forward without the usual headaches.
